lead_paragraph: Novak Djokovic no longer sees winning grand slam titles or staying top of the men’s ATP rankings as a priority in his tennis career, Serbia’s world number one said on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Winning Grand Slams Is No Longer My Priority, Says Djokovic
